      "text": "Albert Einstein once said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2250.0,
      "end_time": 13411.0,
      "text": "\"Everybody's a genius. But if you judge a fish by its ability to climb a tree, it will live it's whole life believing that it is stupid.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 13411.0,
      "end_time": 15231.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen of the jury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
