      "text": "but also makes them climb down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 24182.0,
      "end_time": 26278.0,
      "text": "and do a ten-mile run."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26278.0,
      "end_time": 27332.0,
      "text": "Tell me school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 27332.0,
