      "text": "are you proud of the things you've done?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 29660.0,
      "end_time": 31792.0,
      "text": "Turning millions of people into robots?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 31792.0,
      "end_time": 34313.0,
      "text": "Do you find that fun?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34313.0,
      "end_time": 37250.0,
      "text": "Do you realize how many kids relate to that fish?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 37250.0,
      "end_time": 44424.0,
      "text": "Swimming upstream in class, never finding their gifts, thinking they are stupid, believing they are useless?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44424.0,
      "end_time": 45436.0,
      "text": "Well, the time has come."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 45436.0,
      "end_time": 46501.0,
      "text": "No more excuses."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46501.0,
      "end_time": 53741.0,
      "text": "I call school to the stand and accuse him of killing creativity, individuality, and being intellectually abusive."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53741.0,
      "end_time": 56873.0,
      "text": "He's an ancient institution that has outlived his usage."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56873.0,
      "end_time": 59923.0,
      "text": "So your honor, this concludes my opening statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59923.0,
      "end_time": 62095.0,
      "text": "And if I may present the evidence of my case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62095.0,
