    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 78673.0,
      "end_time": 82714.0,
      "text": "And here's a class we used 150 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 82714.0,
      "end_time": 83983.0,
      "text": "Now ain't that a shame,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 83983.0,
      "end_time": 85823.0,
      "text": "in literally more than a century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 85823.0,
      "end_time": 87525.0,
      "text": "nothing has changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 87525.0,
      "end_time": 90352.0,
      "text": "Yet you claim to prepare students for the future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 90352.0,
      "end_time": 92703.0,
      "text": "But with evidence like that I must ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 92703.0,
      "end_time": 96493.0,
      "text": "do you prepare students for the future or the past?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 96493.0,
      "end_time": 101993.0,
      "text": "I did a background check on you and let the record show that you were made to train people to work in factories."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 101993.0,
      "end_time": 104683.0,
      "text": "Which explains why you put students in straight rows"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 104683.0,
      "end_time": 105343.0,
      "text": "nice and neat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 105343.0,
      "end_time": 107704.0,
      "text": "tell them sit still, raise your hand if you wanna speak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 107704.0,
      "end_time": 108822.0,
      "text": "give them a short break to eat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 108822.0,
      "end_time": 110833.0,
      "text": "and for eight hours a day, tell them what to think."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 110833.0,
      "end_time": 112635.0,
      "text": "Oh, and make them compete to get an A."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 112635.0,
      "end_time": 115398.0,
      "text": "A letter which determines product quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 115398.0,
      "end_time": 117793.0,
      "text": "Hence, grade A of meat."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 117793.0,
      "end_time": 119733.0,
      "text": "I get it. Back then times were different."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 119733.0,
      "end_time": 120694.0,
      "text": "We all have a past."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 120694.0,
      "end_time": 122094.0,
      "text": "And myself ain't no Gandhi."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 122094.0,
      "end_time": 124639.0,
      "text": "But today we don't need to make robots zombies."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 124639.0,
      "end_time": 126140.0,
      "text": "The world has progressed."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 126140.0,
      "end_time": 130686.0,
      "text": "And now we need people who think creatively, innovatively, critically, independently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 130686.0,
      "end_time": 132673.0,
      "text": "with the ability to connect."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 132673.0,
      "end_time": 135765.0,
      "text": "See, every scientist will tell you that no two brains are the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 135765.0,
      "end_time": 138995.0,
      "text": "And every parent with two or more children will confirm that claim."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 138995.0,
      "end_time": 141964.0,
      "text": "So please explain why you treat students like"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 141964.0,
      "end_time": 144455.0,
      "text": "cookie cutter frames or snapback hats?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 144455.0,
      "end_time": 147274.0,
      "text": "Giving them this one size fits all crap?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 147274.0,
      "end_time": 147866.0,
      "text": "Watch your language."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 147866.0,
      "end_time": 148450.0,
      "text": "Sorry your honor."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 148550.0,
      "end_time": 155145.0,
      "text": "But if a doctor prescribes the exact same medicine to all of his patients, the results would be tragic!"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 155184.0,
      "end_time": 156843.0,
      "text": "So many people would get sick. Yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 156843.0,
      "end_time": 159744.0,
      "text": "when it comes to school this is exactly what happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 159744.0,
      "end_time": 162036.0,
      "text": "This educational malpractice."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 162036.0,
      "end_time": 164744.0,
      "text": "Where one teacher stands in front of 20 kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 164744.0,
      "end_time": 168934.0,
      "text": "Each one having different strengths, different needs, different gifts, different dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 168934.0,
      "end_time": 171555.0,
      "text": "And you teach the same thing, the same way?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 171555.0,
      "end_time": 172454.0,
      "text": "That's horrific."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 172454.0,
      "end_time": 175056.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, the defendant should not be acquitted."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 175056.0,
      "end_time": 178005.0,
      "text": "This may be one of the worst criminal offenses ever"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 178005.0,
      "end_time": 179107.0,
      "text": "to be committed."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 179107.0,
      "end_time": 181474.0,
      "text": "And let's mention the ways you treat your employees."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 181474.0,
      "end_time": 182249.0,
      "text": "Objection."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 182249.0,
      "end_time": 183845.0,
      "text": "Overruled. I want to hear this."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 183845.0,
      "end_time": 184705.0,
      "text": "It's a shame."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 184705.0,
      "end_time": 187365.0,
      "text": "I mean teachers have the most important job on the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 187365.0,
      "end_time": 188865.0,
      "text": "yet they're underpaid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 188865.0,
      "end_time": 191665.0,
      "text": "No wonder so many students are short changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 191665.0,
      "end_time": 195235.0,
      "text": "Let's be honest, teaches should earn just as much as doctors."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 195235.0,
      "end_time": 199365.0,
      "text": "Because a doctor can do heart surgery and save the life of a kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 199365.0,
      "end_time": 202224.0,
      "text": "But a great teacher can reach the heart of that kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 202224.0,
      "end_time": 204296.0,
      "text": "and allow him to truly live."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 204296.0,
      "end_time": 206945.0,
      "text": "See, teachers are heroes that often get blamed."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 206945.0,
      "end_time": 208065.0,
      "text": "But they're not the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 208065.0,
      "end_time": 210986.0,
      "text": "They work in a system without many options or rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 210986.0,
      "end_time": 213587.0,
      "text": "Curriculums are created by policy makers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 213587.0,
      "end_time": 216087.0,
      "text": "most of which have never taught a day in their life."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 216087.0,
      "end_time": 218746.0,
      "text": "Just obsessed with standardized tests."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 218746.0,
      "end_time": 222288.0,
      "text": "They think bubbling in a multiple choice test question will determine success."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 222380.0,
      "end_time": 223417.0,
      "text": "That's outlandish."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 223517.0,
      "end_time": 227200.0,
      "text": "In fact, these tests are too crude to be used, and should be abandoned."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 227300.0,
      "end_time": 228740.0,
      "text": "But don't take my word for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 228737.0,
      "end_time": 232586.0,
      "text": "Take Frederick J. Kelly, the man who invented standardized testing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 232586.0,
      "end_time": 237605.0,
      "text": "who said, and I quote, \"These tests are too crude to be used, and should be abandoned.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 237605.0,
      "end_time": 238835.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen of the jury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 238930.0,
      "end_time": 242150.0,
      "text": "if we continue down this road, the results will be lethal."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 242136.0,
      "end_time": 246176.0,
      "text": "I don't have much faith in school, but I do have faith in people."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 246176.0,
      "end_time": 250077.0,
      "text": "And if we can customize health care, cars, and Facebook pages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 250077.0,
      "end_time": 252776.0,
      "text": "then it is our duty to do the same for education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 252776.0,
      "end_time": 256055.0,
      "text": "to upgrade it, change it, do away with school spirit."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 256055.0,
      "end_time": 257408.0,
      "text": "'Cause that's useless."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 257408.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261197.00000000003,
      "text": "Unless we're working to bring the spirit out of each and every student."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 261197.0,
      "end_time": 262447.0,
      "text": "That should be our task."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 262447.0,
      "end_time": 264197.0,
      "text": "No more common core."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 264197.0,
      "end_time": 267857.0,
      "text": "Instead, let's reach the core of every heart in every class."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 267857.0,
      "end_time": 271607.0,
      "text": "Sure, math is important. But no more than art or dance."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 271607.0,
      "end_time": 273667.0,
      "text": "Let's give every gift an equal chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 273667.0,
      "end_time": 278077.0,
      "text": "I know this sounds like a dream, but countries like Finland are doing impressive things."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 278077.0,
      "end_time": 281527.0,
      "text": "They have shorter school days. Teachers make a decent wage."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 281527.0,
      "end_time": 286447.0,
      "text": "Homework is non existent and they focus on collaboration instead of competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 286447.0,
      "end_time": 288197.0,
      "text": "But here's the kicker boys and girls."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 288197.0,
      "end_time": 293186.0,
      "text": "Their educational system outperforms every other country in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 293186.0,
      "end_time": 296206.0,
      "text": "Other places like Singapore, succeeding rapidly."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 296206.0,
      "end_time": 299667.0,
      "text": "Schools like Montessori. Programs like Khan Academy."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 299667.0,
      "end_time": 302618.0,
      "text": "There is no single solution. But let's get moving."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 302618.0,
      "end_time": 305927.0,
      "text": "Because while students may be 20% of our population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 305927.0,
      "end_time": 308707.0,
      "text": "they are 100% of our future."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 308707.0,
      "end_time": 310628.0,
      "text": "So let's attend to their dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 310628.0,
      "end_time": 312847.0,
      "text": "And there's no telling what we can achieve."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 312847.0,
      "end_time": 314938.0,
      "text": "This is a world in which I believe."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 314938.0,
      "end_time": 320388.0,
      "text": "A world where fish are no longer forced to climb trees."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 320388.0,
      "end_time": 321928.0,
      "text": "I rest my case."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 333968.0,
      "end_time": 338437.0,
      "text": "Hey guys, my name is Prince EA, and I want to say thank you so much for watching my video."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 338437.0,
      "end_time": 340877.0,
      "text": "But now, I want to know what you think."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 340877.0,
      "end_time": 347515.0,
      "text": "How can we together, create a more efficient, effective, and just better future of learning."
